reviewText: I enjoyed this, good info, mostly Biblical accurate.  Not sure it proved it's name though.

To be continued is when is so good we want to see MORE. With proper editing he could have had the second part which should be more informative out there. It needed editing

A collection of 11-films that are biblical in nature as shown on 3-DVD disc's. The films are in both: Color and black-n-white. And, some are considered rare and hard to find movies, that are also considered to be: "Classic Epics." The running time on each film, varies. So, pop the popcorn and make a weekend of it. Enjoy! Nina Kish
I love any movie that spreads the word of Jesus Christ and the Resurrection.  God Bless all who watch it.
